{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/add-new-properties-to-a-javascript-object","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Dodajte Nova Svojstva JavaScript Objektu","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Nova svojstva postojecim JavaScript objektima mozete dodati na isti nacin kao sto ih menjate.</p>\n<p>Ovako dodajemo svojstvo <code>bark</code> objektu <code>ourDog</code>:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">ourDog.bark = \"bow-wow\";\n</code></pre>\n<p>au</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">ourDog[\"bark\"] = \"bow-wow\";\n</code></pre>\n<p>Kada sada proverimo <code>ourDog.bark</code>, dobicemo zvuk lajanja, <code>bow-wow</code>.</p>\n<p>Primer:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">const ourDog = {\n  \"name\": \"Camper\",\n  \"legs\": 4,\n  \"tails\": 1,\n  \"friends\": [\"everything!\"]\n};\n\nourDog.bark = \"bow-wow\";\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"56bbb991ad1ed5201cd392d2","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Dodajte svojstvo <code>bark</code> objektu <code>myDog</code> i postavite ga na zvuk psa, kao \"woof\". Mozete koristiti notaciju tacke ili uglastih zagrada.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301169,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/add-new-properties-to-a-javascript-object"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"const myDog = {\n  \"name\": \"Happy Coder\",\n  \"legs\": 4,\n  \"tails\": 1,\n  \"friends\": [\"freeCodeCamp Campers\"]\n};\n\n","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Treba da dodate svojstvo <code>bark</code> objektu <code>myDog</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(myDog.bark !== undefined);"},{"text":"<p>Ne treba da dodate <code>bark</code> u samoj inicijalizaciji <code>myDog</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(!/bark[^\\n]:/.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-javascript","dashedName":"add-new-properties-to-a-javascript-object","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-javascript","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/delete-properties-from-a-javascript-object","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/updating-object-properties","id":"56bbb991ad1ed5201cd392d2","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum) {\n  if (endNum - startNum === 0) {\n    return [startNum];\n  } else {\n    const numbers = rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum - 1);\n    numbers.push(endNum);\n    return numbers;\n  }\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/add-new-properties-to-a-javascript-object"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}